				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p97618">Re: High color bitmap on the SNES</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=97618#p97618"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Aug 04, 2012 9:10 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
